title: Does (Accidentally) Doing This Make You The Worst Kind Of Friend?
description:
It's Cassie's birthday! Her fam threw her a cute little British tea party (they're British, in case you didn't know), and then Cassie recalls the time she completely blew her friend's surprise party out of the water by complete accident...and she got some karma dished out.
